### Test SSE Chat Completions with Client Tool (should be ignored)

POST http://localhost:4001/api/openai/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: replace-with-shared-frontend-backend-key

{
  "model": "current_model.gguf",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Open a modal"
    }
  ],
  "stream": true,
  "tools": [
    {
      "type": "function",
      "function": {
        "name": "client__open_modal",
        "description": "Open a modal dialog in the UI",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "title": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}